ory/Teacher-Murdered/gZ9YI7q0EECNTamcw5jTHw.cspx |title=Teacher Murdered |publisher=Cbs42.com |accessdate=2011-03-12 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110718230239/http://www.cbs42.com/mostpopular/story/Teacher-Murdered/gZ9YI7q0EECNTamcw5jTHw.cspx |archivedate=2011-07-18 }}</ref>\n|-\n| January 26, 2010\n| [[Eastern Cape|Ngqeleni]],<br>[[Eastern Cape]],<br>South Africa\n| Unknown, 25\n| 2 dead\n| 1 injured\n| After an argument, a 25-year-old man shot and seriously wounded his girlfriend, who was working as a clerk at Jongingaba Junior-Secondary School. A 12-year-old girl was also killed inside a classroom by a stray bullet, before the gunman tried to escape. He was later caught and killed by an angry mob.<ref>[http://www.news24.com/Content/SouthAfrica/News/1059/8526be9c69ba4fd9b2d2bf4b0c089f1d/26-01-2010-05-30/Girl,_12,_shot_dead_at_school Girl, 12, shot dead at school] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100129180600/http://www.news24.com/Content/SouthAfrica/News/1059/8526be9c69ba4fd9b2d2bf4b0c089f1d/26-01-2010-05-30/Girl%2C_12%2C_shot_dead_at_school |date=2010-01-29 }}, ''[[News24]]'' (January 26, 2010)</ref>\n|-\n| February 5, 2010\n| [[Madison, Alabama|Madison]],<br>[[Alabama]],<br>United States\n| Hammad Memon, 14\n| 1 dead\n|\n| Todd Brown, a 14-year-old ninth-grade student, was shot in the back of the head in a hallway of Discovery Middle School in [[Madison, Alabama]] by another student, Hammad Memon. Brown was transported to a hospital in [[Huntsville, Alabama]] where he later died. In May 2013, Memon plead guilty to the murder of Brown, and was sentenced to 30 years of prison. After Memon is released from prison, he is likely to be deported to his native [[Pakistan]].<ref>{{cite news|url=http://blog.al.com/breaking/2013/05/hammad_memon_pleads_guilty_to.html |title=Hammad Memon pleads guilty to murder, sentenced to 30 years for 2010 shooting death of 14-year-old classmate at Discovery Middle |publisher=Al.com |date=May 28, 2013 |accessdate=June 14, 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2010/CRIME/02/06/alabama.student.killed/ |title=Ninth-grader fatally shot by classmate at Alabama school |publisher=cnn.com |date=2010-02-06 |accessdate=2011-03-12}}</ref>\n|-\n| February 15, 2010\n| [[Shorncliffe, Queensland|Shorncliffe]],<br>[[Queensland]],<br>Australia\n| ..., 13\n| 1 dead\n|\n| Elliot Fletcher, a 12-year-old boy, was stabbed and killed on the grounds of [[St Patrick's College, Shorncliffe|St Patrick's College]] by a 13-year-old classmate.<ref>{{cite news|last=Ironside |first=Robyn |url=http://www.news.com.au/national/boy-stabbed-in-schoolyard-at-st-patricks-college-shorncliffe/story-e6frfkvr-1225830429705 |title=Boy stabbed in schoolyard at St Patrick's College |publisher=News.com.au |date=2010-02-15 |accessdate=2011-03-12}}</ref> The two students were involved in an argument on the playground of the Catholic school before the stabbing took place.<ref>{{cite news|author1=Robyn Ironside  |author2=Anna Caldwell  |lastauthoramp=yes|url=http://www.news.com.au/couriermail/story/0,23739,26729130-952,00.html |title=Elliott Fletcher slain at St Patrick's College |publisher=News.com.au |date=2010-02-16 |accessdate=2011-03-12}}</ref>\n|-\n| February 18, 2010\n| [[Ludwigshafen]],<br>[[Rhineland-Palatinate]]<br>Germany\n| Florian K., 23\n| 1 dead\n|\n| Florian K., a 23-year-old former student armed with a knife and a starter pistol, stabbed and killed his former 58-year-old teacher at the vocational school \"Technik 2\" in Ludwigshafen. He was arrested shortly after. He was reportedly upset at the teacher for giving him low grades while he was a student at the school.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.stern.de/panorama/bluttat-in-ludwigshafener-berufsschule-ex-schueler-stach-aus-wut-zu-1544645.html |title=Ex-Sch\u00fcler stach aus Wut zu |publisher=Stern.de |date=2010-02-18 |accessdate=2011-03-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://calgaryherald.com/news/Teacher+stabbed+death+over+marks/2584039/story.html|title=Teacher stabbed to death over 'bad marks'|accessdate=10 January 2020}}</ref> Eight months later he was convicted of murder and sentenced to 14 years in prison and placement in a psychiatric facility.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.spiegel.de/panorama/justiz/0,1518,724262,00.html |title=Gericht verurteilt Ex-Sch\u00fcler zu 14 Jahren Haft |publisher=Spiegel.de |accessdate=2011-03-12}}</ref>\n|-\n| February 23, 2010\n| [[Littleton, Colorado|Littleton]],<br>[[Colorado]],<br>United States\n| Bruco Strong Eagle Eastwood, 32\n|\n| 2 injured\n| A 32-year-old gunman, identified as Bruco Strong Eagle Eastwood, armed with a [[.30-06]] [[Winchester Model 70]] [[bolt-action rifle]], opened fire on students at [[Deer Creek Middle School]] at 3:30 pm (MST) as school was being let out in [[Littleton, Colorado]]. The gunman was later tackled by a math teacher and the teacher turned him into the police when they arrived on scene. The gunman shot and injured two students at the school before he was taken into custody. Eastwood was placed into a mental health facility for life.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/two-teens-injured-in-colorado-school-shooting/article1479363/ |title=Two teens injured in Colorado school shooting |publisher=Theglobeandmail.com |accessdate=2011-03-12 |location=Toronto |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100227030853/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/two-teens-injured-in-colorado-school-shooting/article1479363/ |archivedate=February 27, 2010 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2010/CRIME/02/24/colorado.school.shooting/?hpt=T2 |title=School shooting suspect identified |publisher=Cnn.com |date=2010-02-24 |accessdate=2011-03-12}}</ref>\n|-\n| March 17, 2010\n| [[Deerfield Beach]],<br>[[Florida]]<br>United States\n| Wayne Treacy, 15\n|\n| 1 injured\n| 15-year-old Wayne Treacy stomped and kicked 15-year-old Josie Lou Ratley's head repeatedly with steel-toed boots. T