091019100830/http://www.thebostonchannel.com/news/21313592/detail.html |archivedate=October 19, 2009 }}</ref>\n|-\n| March 7, 2007\n| [[Midland, Michigan]], United States\n| David Turner, 17\n| 1 dead\n| 1 injured\n| 17-year-old David Turner [[n:One dead in Michigan school shooting|shot and critically wounded 17-year old Jessica Forsyth]] four times outside [[Herbert Henry Dow High School]] before killing himself in the parking lot.\n|-\n| March 17, 2007\n| [[Saba Yoi District]], [[Thailand]]\n|\n| 3 dead\n| 7 injured\n| A number of attackers threw explosives and fired numerous bullets at an [[Islamic]] school killing 3 teens and injured 7 others who were sleeping.<ref>{{cite news|title=Muslim Villagers Riot in Thailand After Attackers Kill 3 Children at Islamic School|url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/2007/03/18/muslim-villagers-riot-in-thailand-after-attackers-kill-3-children-at-islamic/ |work=Fox News | date=March 18, 2007}}</ref> \n|-\n| April 10, 2007\n| [[Gresham, Oregon]], United States\n| Chad Escobedo, 15\n|\n| 10 injured\n| High school freshman Chad Escobedo shoots the windows out of two classrooms from outside Springwater Trail High School injuring ten students with [[Fragmentation (weaponry)|shrapnel]] and broken glass, two of which required stitches. His motive was to shoot at a class in which he was enrolled, unhappy that the instructor had called his parents; the classrooms he hit, however, were not his intended target.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theoutlookonline.com/news/story.php?story_id=117652056556535900 |title=Shooter was \u2018crying out for help,\u2019 friends say |publisher=Theoutlookonline.com |accessdate=2011-03-12}}</ref>\n|-\n| April 18, 2007\n| [[Huntersville, North Carolina]], United States\n| Josh Emerson Cook, 16\n| 1 dead\n|\n| A 16-year-old threatened two students in the parking lot at North Mecklenberg High School with a gun, and shortly afterwards, had shot himself at a local gas station when confronted by police.<ref>{{Cite web