alabama.student.killed/ |title=Ninth-grader fatally shot by classmate at Alabama school |publisher=cnn.com |date=2010-02-06 |accessdate=2011-03-12}}</ref>\n|-\n| February 15, 2010\n| [[Shorncliffe, Queensland|Shorncliffe]],<br>[[Queensland]],<br>Australia\n| ..., 13\n| 1 dead\n|\n| Elliot Fletcher, a 12-year-old boy, was stabbed and killed on the grounds of [[St Patrick's College, Shorncliffe|St Patrick's College]] by a 13-year-old classmate.<ref>{{cite news|last=Ironside |first=Robyn |url=http://www.news.com.au/national/boy-stabbed-in-schoolyard-at-st-patricks-college-shorncliffe/story-e6frfkvr-1225830429705 |title=Boy stabbed in schoolyard at St Patrick's College |publisher=News.com.au |date=2010-02-15 |accessdate=2011-03-12}}</ref> The two students were involved in an argument on the playground of the Catholic school before the stabbing took place.<ref>{{cite news|author1=Robyn Ironside  |author2=Anna Caldwell  |lastauthoramp=yes|url=http://www.news.com.au/couriermail/story/0,23739,26729130-952,00.html |title=Elliott Fletcher slain at St Patrick's College |publisher=News.com.au |date=2010-02-16 |accessdate=2011-03-12}}</ref>\n|-\n| February 18, 2010\n| [[Ludwigshafen]],<br>[[Rhineland-Palatinate]]<br>Germany\n| Florian K., 23\n| 1 dead\n|\n| Florian K., a 23-year-old former student armed with a knife and a starter pistol, stabbed and killed his former 58-year-old teacher at the vocational school \"Technik 2\" in Ludwigshafen. He was arrested shortly after. He was reportedly upset at the teacher for giving him low grades while he was a student at the school.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.stern.de/panorama/bluttat-in-ludwigshafener-berufsschule-ex-schueler-stach-aus-wut-zu-1544645.html |title=Ex-Sch\u00fcler stach aus Wut zu |publisher=Stern.de |date=2010-02-18 |accessdate=2011-03-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://calgaryherald.com/news/Teacher+stabbed+death+over+marks/2584039/story.html|title=Teacher stabbed to death over 'bad marks'|accessdate=10 January 2020