ailyarchive/2010_07/071210.htm#story2 |archivedate=2010-11-25 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=http://www.ticotimes.net/ |url=http://www.ticotimes.net/dailyarchive/2010_07/0706102.cfm |title=Educators respond to an attempted murder in Heredia high school |publisher=Ticotimes.net |date=2010-07-06 |accessdate=2011-03-12 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110119142345/http://www.ticotimes.net/dailyarchive/2010_07/0706102.cfm |archivedate=2011-01-19 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ticotimes.net/News/Daily-News/17-Year-Old-Goes-On-Trial-for-Death-of-School-Principal_Wednesday-October-27-2010 |title=17-Year-Old Goes On Trial for Death of School Principal |publisher=Ticotimes.net |date=2010-10-27 |accessdate=2011-03-12 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101104044913/http://www.ticotimes.net/News/Daily-News/17-Year-Old-Goes-On-Trial-for-Death-of-School-Principal_Wednesday-October-27-2010/ |archivedate=2010-11-04 }}</ref>\n|-\n| July 2, 2010\n| [[London]], [[England]], [[United Kingdom]] \n| Three people\n| 1 dead\n| 1 injured\n| A 15-year-old student was stabbed to death during a fight at Park Campus School, an alternative school. Another teenager was hospitalized for minor wounds. Three people were arrested.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2010/jul/02/west-norwood-school-stabbing |title=15-year-old schoolboy stabbed to death in south London|newspaper=[[The Guardian]]|date=July 2, 2010 |accessdate=September 2, 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n| August 30, 2010\n| [[Blountville]],<br>[[Tennessee]],<br>United States\n| Thomas Cowan, 62\n| 1 dead\n|\n| Thomas Cowan entered [[Sullivan Central High School]] with two loaded guns intent on killing principal Melanie Riden. SRO Carolyn Gudger was able to hold him off until back-up arrived, when they were forced to shoot and kill Cowan. No staff or students were injured.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/id/38923637 |title=Armed man fatally shot at Tenn. high school |